      "answer_en": "Hi, Mokkaya provide some 2 options as a payment method, that are online transfer method, and COD payment method.\n1. COD payment = a method that you don't need to pay anything in advance. Your customer will need to pay it prior to receiving the package from courier. Later, the profit margin will be transferred to you by Mokkaya.\n2. Online transfer = the method that you need to pay the order in advance, by transferring to designated bank accounts in order to get it processed. The difference between the amount you collect from your buyer and the the amount that you pay for the order is your margin, so if you use this method, be sure you already mark-up the price when you bill the payment to your buyer.\n",
