      "question_en": "Why I can't use COD?",
      "answer_en": "Hi, there are several reasons that makes you (or any other resellers) cannot use COD as follow:\n1. The order price is equal to or greater than Rp5.000.000.\n2. The product you choose doesn't support COD method (make sure the product has COD label on it).\n3. The recipient address does not support COD delivery by the expedition.\n4. You've used all your daily quota. \n5. Your COD feature is being blocked by admin because of any violation you ever made, such as making fake orders with COD method.\n6. Your COD feature is being blocked automatically by system due to having too many rejected orders.",
